---
title: Lemon Pepper Salmon & Autumn Veggie Toss  with Baby Leaves & Balsamic Glaze
description: Salmon is always nice cooked with light flavours, but a dark and rich balsamic glaze with delicious root veggies in a cosy and vibrant toss might be the new best way to eat salmon.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65c30546611ea70d817f0a68-9e77686c.jpeg
